# Roles and Responsibilities

## User
Represents individuals who register on the platform to browse and purchase products.

Responsibilities:
- Register and login
- Browse products
- Add products to cart
- Place orders
- Track order history

---

## Admin
Responsible for managing the platform.

Responsibilities:
- Manage product categories
- Upload banner images
- Add / update / delete products
- Monitor orders
- View analytics

---

## Products
Represents all items available on the platform.

Details stored:
- Product name
- Description
- Price
- Category
- Stock availability

---

## Cart
Stores products added by users before checkout.

Features:
- Add items
- Remove items
- Update quantity
- View total price

---

## Orders
Stores all orders placed by users.

Details:
- User ID
- Product list
- Order status
- Payment status
- Delivery details
